<task id="task-5575" class="- topic/topic task/task "><title class="- topic/title ">In manual view</title><taskbody class="- topic/body task/taskbody "><steps class="- topic/ol task/steps "><step class="- topic/li task/step "><cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">Open a test case in&#160;<uicontrol conkeyref="ks-UI-text/ks-ui-manual" class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol "/>&#160;view. Click on the drop-down icon of the&#160;<uicontrol conkeyref="ks-UI-text/ks-ui-add" class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol "/> button, then choose <uicontrol conkeyref="ks-UI-text/ks-ui-method-call-statements" class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol "/>.</cmd></step><step class="- topic/li task/step "><cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">To add a keyword under a statement, select that statement, then click <uicontrol conkeyref="ks-UI-text/ks-ui-add" class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol "/> . A test step is created under that statement.</cmd><info class="- topic/itemgroup task/info "><image width="300" href="../Images/method-call.png" class="- topic/image "><alt class="- topic/alt ">Method call statement</alt></image></info><stepresult class="- topic/itemgroup task/stepresult ">A test step representing a method call  is added to the test case.<p class="- topic/p "><image width="600" href="../Images/830-method-call-statement.png" class="- topic/image "><alt class="- topic/alt ">add binary statement</alt></image></p></stepresult></step><step class="- topic/li task/step "><cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">Double-click on the <uicontrol conkeyref="ks-UI-text/ks-ui-input" class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol "/> cell to edit the called method.</cmd><info class="- topic/itemgroup task/info "><image width="600" href="../Images/method-call-input.png" class="- topic/image "><alt class="- topic/alt ">Method call input</alt></image></info></step><step class="- topic/li task/step "><cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">Save the test case when you're done. </cmd></step></steps></taskbody></task>